  "storelongdescription": "<h2 style='color:#a0d8cc; font-size:28px; margin-bottom:10px;'>Flow Center Dock</h2><p style='font-size:16px; color:#e0e0e0; line-height:1.5;'>Flow Center Dock brings a smooth, glassy animated interface with a centered dock at the bottom. A light and minimal New tab layout.</p><p style='font-size:16px; color:#e0e0e0; line-height:1.5;'><strong>Customize</strong> <br>Adjust maximum bookmarks by changing local storage values<br><br><code style='background:#2a3a3a; padding:4px 6px; border-radius:4px; display:inline-block; margin:6px 0; color:#a0d8cc;'>set localstorage.MAX_BOOKMARKS = 15;<br>set localstorage.layoutPattern = 15;</code><br>Increase or decrease the value to your preference. [not recommended to go above 15]</p>",
